<p>We’re going to play a game with a fair coin. We’ll flip the coin, generating a sequence, until one of two sequences occurs:</p>

<p>HHHH comes up (Player A wins)</p>

<p>THHH comes up (Player B wins)</p>

<p>What is player A’s probability of winning?</p>
